{"tid":2417881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T10:52:30.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9e009c7a9032cd901168d1c3f9bd225dbec321cd","tid":2417881,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"【愛國者治港】港澳辦夏寶龍：反對中共不是愛國者　中央主導更改選舉制度　阻反中亂港者入局<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37AruGi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37AruGi&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=fa5a1cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37AruGi</a><br />\n<br />\n北京持續收緊對港管治，預料將大規模改變選舉制度，港澳辦主任夏寶龍今早在研討會上，再次重申要由「愛國者治港」。他指出，「愛國者治港」是港人治港的「最低標準」，重要崗位在「任何情況下」都不能被反中亂港分子佔據，他更列出「愛國者」的條件，指歇斯底里攻擊中央、公開宣揚港獨、在國際「唱衰」香港、要求外國制裁、觸犯國安法，以及「攬炒派」，都不是愛國者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXNDv8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXNDv8v.jpg&h=9ffe212c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家佢就係大巴大巴車落D留港抗爭撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問你可以點樣抗爭？抗條撚咩，淨係安心出行香港人都已經擋唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n客觀現實就係得兩個選擇，第一個走，第二個留低接受"},{"pid":"7816ca8c74e69d0e0d6665fd74187a28743c5a0f","tid":2417881,"uid":114193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"連下sir 唔係話唔好理香港變成點嘅咩？<br />\n做乜仲出咁多新聞post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想做港豬順民架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後作為連下sir 信徒<br />\n幫手推廣下佢嘅概念<br />\n俾連登班黑暴知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9a9d67279c8d1a7e1bdfe5e39b1e4476e56de216","tid":2417881,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"你問完我點睇<br />\n另一班人又問移民當抗爭撚點睇<br />\n<br />\n點做都俾人屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a689917af3ebb94d05a0e35df100ed014eb44af","tid":2417881,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"新加坡式權威管治！"},{"pid":"9a5a0c340f8a5107c05c496f33de8e4f25d827d5","tid":2417881,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a689917af3ebb94d05a0e35df100ed014eb44af","tid":2417881,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"新加坡式權威管治！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"新加坡邊有咁閪"},{"pid":"06ec73fc36ace5c84aa15d28b6b441c34573f88d","tid":2417881,"uid":229607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a9d67279c8d1a7e1bdfe5e39b1e4476e56de216","tid":2417881,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"你問完我點睇<br />\n另一班人又問移民當抗爭撚點睇<br />\n<br />\n點做都俾人屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"算啦，都係想搞分化姐<br />\n<br />\n走定留都有人讚有人彈<br />\n<br />\n總之自己想點咪點<br />\n<br />\n你唔想走既話，唔通佢叫你走你就違背意願跟住走咩，咁同家長政策有咩分別"},{"pid":"08ea242bd5ad572282dff1df63af0e3b145b5ac1","tid":2417881,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a5a0c340f8a5107c05c496f33de8e4f25d827d5","tid":2417881,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a689917af3ebb94d05a0e35df100ed014eb44af","tid":2417881,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"新加坡式權威管治！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"新加坡邊有咁閪"}